               <H2>Market Summary</H2>
               <p>Westmount Shopping Centre features a newly built, exterior 41,000 square foot, eleven screen Cineplex Theatre which includes a VIP lounge – the first of its kind in London, ON.   An enhanced capacity London Transit Bus terminal situated along Viscount Road provides a western terminus point to several routes and is part of the City of London’s long term public transportation plans.  Shoeless Joe’s first London location.  The upper level of the centre welcomes professional and medical offices and the lower level has been reconfigured to enhance its former retail shopping experience.</p>
               <br>
               <strong>Total GLA:  </strong>561,792 square feet <br><br>
               
               
              
         
          
